output_list.description: Integer overflow in distribute function allows unauthorized increase of tokens, aka 'distributeOverflow' issue.
Wrong Logic in transferFrom function allows attackers to steal arbitrary amounts of tokens, aka 'wrongLogic' issue.
Bad Randomness in PayWinner function allows attackers to always win, aka 'badRandomness' issue.
Access Control in ToOwner function allows attackers to claim contract ownership, aka 'accessControl' issue.
Typo Constructor in MorphToken function allows attackers to exploit constructor naming vulnerability, aka 'typoConstructor' issue.
